data.description: Welcome to Llano, home of the quaint community of Crystalaire.  As you step into this spacious home, you will be captivated with the formal entry and a welllaid out floor plan. This custom-built home boasts 3 bedrooms.and 2 baths.This is not your typical split floor plan; the bedrooms are in front and rear making the living space perfect of gatherings and entertaining. The kitchen features granite/tile countertops, center island w/seating, nice cabinetry, a garden window, center island, and a dining area with lots of sunlight. The scenic half-acre corner lot with Mature Shade trees has been professionally Landscaped. Enjoy the Fenced Backyard with its Water Fountain, Pergola, Grape Arbor and Garden including many Fruit Trees. The Rock Walls were created to simulate the feeling you get at the Abbey.Want to live in a Country Club community and Golf all the time? Awarded renowned eighteen-hole golf course community of Crystalaire is the place to live so just bring your clubs and enjoy all the amenities with a Golf or Social membership to this private club in the beautiful foothills of the San Gabriel foothills.
